1022
01:20:10,100 --> 01:20:10,810
Busted!

1023
01:20:10,810 --> 01:20:13,390
Why you gotta be like that?

1024
01:20:14,200 --> 01:20:24,900
- [Laughing]
- [Laughing]

1025
01:20:27,380 --> 01:20:29,120
Hey, Mitsuha.

1026
01:20:29,120 --> 01:20:31,200
You still have a lot to do.

1027
01:20:31,200 --> 01:20:32,760
Listen.

1028
01:20:32,760 --> 01:20:35,410
- It's coming.
- Don't worry.

1029
01:20:35,410 --> 01:20:37,760
- You still have enough time.
- [Nod]

1030
01:20:37,760 --> 01:20:39,700
I'll do my best.

1031
01:20:40,620 --> 01:20:43,410
