did I even come here for?

1056
01:22:08,930 --> 01:22:09,910
I came...

1057
01:22:09,910 --> 01:22:12,180
I came all this way to see her!

1058
01:22:12,180 --> 01:22:13,930
I came to save her!

1059
01:22:13,930 --> 01:22:16,110
